metadata.name: Strengthened / Persistent #11
metadata.description: Don't waste your time on what doesn't really matter / All bad times are fleeting and stay as long as we let them be / If you learn from mistakes, consider yourself someone strong; If you learn the lessons, consider yourself intelligent / Don't hesitate, don't think so much, do it now.

metadata.description:
"Siena" is a generative abstract artwork made with p5js and custom shaders

Based on my previous experience, known patterns and existing style preferences
Artwork is 100% code, no images used.

CONTROLS

- S: Save a png file with the current resolution

metadata.name: RIP HEN CITY #70
metadata.description:
4 #RIPhen #StillHereNow

---

HEADLINES

futuristic cities, reconstruction, rebuilding, community resonances

---

DETAILS 

Image composition 

92 layers:
55 different image: 54 Ai rendered - Stable Diffusion + 1 GENESIS - Initial Image:

'Spatial breakdown_III' - 2010, oil on canvas,  50 x 70 cm 

All images are related to this artwork.

*** The GENESIS, the pixel image made from my oil painting, was also included. ***


WORKFLOW

1 - I created the oil painting.

2 - It was dropped into Stable Diffusion as an initial image. - The original renders will be minted soon on objktcom.

3 - I added H=N logo's blocks to the subdivision.

--- I studied forms and shapes with Ai ---

metadata.name: Reversed #40
metadata.description:
This collection captures the spirit of the mountains, where the ridge blends into sky and earth. The inversion of the image evokes the philosophy that sometimes, to better understand nature and art, you have to look at things from a different angle, to reveal a new perspective, a new balance.

##Features
Palette, Moon, Stars, BlendMode, Negative Mode.

Made with p5js
